OL,3,CChildren dragged and abused by staff
OL,4,Cat Coventry Hospital, health watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FStaff at a hospital in Coventry were
OL,8,Fcaught on CCTV "dragging" and
OL,9,Fphysically abusing children, according
OL,10,Fto a health watchdog report.
OL,12,FThe Care Quality Commission inspection
OL,13,Ffound that children were being
OL,14,Fphysically abused at the Cygnet Joyce
OL,15,FParker Hospital in Coventry, in July
OL,16,Flast year.
