OL,3,CChildren dragged and abused by staff
OL,4,Cat Coventry Hospital, health watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt said a child at the hospital told
OL,8,Finspectors that staff at the mental
OL,9,Fhealth unit "sometimes bent their
OL,10,Fwrist" and that they were hurt by
OL,11,Fstaff "twisting their knee" on one
OL,12,Foccasion.
OL,14,FThe report said footage of the
OL,15,Fincidents identified 12 members of
OL,16,Fstaff as "passive bystanders" who did
OL,17,Fnot raise concerns.
