OL,4,Cat Coventry Hospital, health watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe CQC report said: "We reviewed
OL,8,Fclosed-circuit television footage for
OL,9,Fthree incidents of restraint where
OL,10,Fchildren and young people were
OL,11,Fphysically abused by staff. Staff were
OL,12,Fobserved dragging children and young
OL,13,Fpeople during these incidents.
OL,15,F"For all three incidents reviewed,
OL,16,Fthere was no apparent risk requiring
OL,17,Frestraint presented by the young
OL,18,Fperson.
