OL,3,CChildren dragged and abused by staff
OL,4,Cat Coventry Hospital, health watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"There was no evidence of staff
OL,8,Fattempting de-escalation prior to
OL,9,Frestraining the children and young
OL,10,Fpeople. In one incident staff
OL,11,Fescalated the situation by refusing
OL,12,Fthe young person access to their
OL,13,Fbedroom."
OL,15,FFour out of seven children were spoken
OL,16,Fto during the inspection and they did
OL,17,Fnot "feel safe at the service".
