OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FPatients also raised concerns about
OL,8,Fagency staff who were not "kind and
OL,9,Fskilled to support them when they were
OL,10,Fdistressed."
OL,12,FThe CQC said three warning notices
OL,13,Fwere sent to the hospital after the
OL,14,Finspection in July for "failing to
OL,15,Fmeet regulations relating to staff
OL,16,Fabuse of children and young people
OL,17,Fduring incidents of restraint".
