OL,4,Cat Coventry Hospital, health watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"We continue to strongly refute any
OL,8,Fallegations of abuse. The police and
OL,9,Flocal safeguarding authorities have
OL,10,Fclosed their investigations into a
OL,11,Fsmall number of safeguarding incidents
OL,12,Fthat we reported to them last summer,
OL,13,Fand they concluded no further action
OL,14,Fwill be taken.
OL,16,F"After careful consideration last
OL,17,FSeptember, we made the decision to
OL,18,Fchange the services offered at Cygnet
OL,19,FJoyce Parker Hospital and to
OL,20,Fdiscontinue our Child and Adolescent
OL,21,FMental Health provision at the site.
