OL,4,Cat Coventry Hospital, health watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe hospital, which had four wards and
OL,8,Fwas run by Cygnet Health Care Limited,
OL,9,Fhas changed its use since the
OL,10,Finspection and now only provides
OL,11,Fservices to adult male patients.
OL,13,FDespite its change of use, the CQC
OL,14,Fsaid the hospital is still registered
OL,15,Fto be able to provide mental health
OL,16,Fservices to children and adolescents.
OL,18,FNo new ratings for the hospital have
OL,19,Fbeen issued by the watchdog and it
OL,20,Fremains rated "requires improvement".
